  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个状态图，展示从基础设施层到应用层的部署依赖关系。核心是从Infra_EtcdCluster开始，它直接关联到Developer角色。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Developer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，Infra_EtcdCluster作为基础设施的存储后端，Developer是操作它的角色。那Developer还需要连到其他节点吗？比如实际的Infrastructure资源？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Developer",
        "Infrastructure"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Developer要同时连到Infrastructure。另外还有一个关键点——Developer需要管理configMap，这是配置管理的核心环节。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Developer",
        "Infrastructure",
        "configMap"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我现在把这三条关系加上：Infra_EtcdCluster到Developer，Developer到Infrastructure，Developer到configMap。接下来configMap应该流向哪里？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Developer",
        "Infrastructure",
        "configMap"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "configMap需要被Infrastructure消费，同时configMap也要同步到Kubernetes集群。这是配置从静态定义到运行时生效的转换。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "configMap",
        "Infrastructure",
        "Kubernetes"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "所以是双向的：Infrastructure--configMap，以及configMap--Kubernetes。然后Kubernetes作为编排层，应该支撑上层的Application对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infrastructure",
        "configMap",
        "Kubernetes",
        "Application"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，Kubernetes到Application。最后还有一个闭环——Application运行时需要回连到Infra_EtcdCluster，比如服务发现或者状态存储。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Kubernetes",
        "Application",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成。整个链路形成了闭环：从底层Infra_EtcdCluster出发，经过Developer操作、configMap配置流转、Kubernetes编排，最终Application运行时再依赖回etcd集群。我检查一下各节点连接是否完整。",
      "elements_involved": [
